#. Tag: title
#: intro.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "आमुख"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: intro.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kmail; Welcome Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<स्क्रीनसूचना>&kmail; स्वागतम् पटल</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: intro.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kmail; Welcome Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<वाक्यांश>&kmail; स्वागतम् पटल</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kmail; Welcome Screen</para>"
msgstr "<परा>&kmail; स्वागत पटल</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kmail; Team welcomes you to &kmail;, a user-friendly email client by "
"&kde;. Our goal is to make &kmail; a program that is both beautiful and "
"intuitive without sacrificing power."
msgstr ""
"इति &kmail; दलं भवतः स्वागतं करोति &kmail;, &kde;द्वारा उपयोक्तृ-अनुकूलं ईमेल-ग्राहकं । "
"अस्माकं लक्ष्यं &kmail; शक्तित्यागं विना सुन्दरः सहजज्ञानयुक्तः च कार्यक्रमः।"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have never set up an email client on a &UNIX; system before, we "
"suggest that you read through the <link linkend=\"getting-started\">Getting "
"Started</link> section first."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् कदापि &amp;UNIX; system before, वयं सुझावमिदं दद्मः यत् भवान् पठतु<link "
"linkend=\"getting-started\"> आरम्भः</link> खण्डः प्रथमं ।"

#. Tag: title
#: intro.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some &kmail; Features"
msgstr "केचन &kmail; गुणाः"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is a brief guide to some of the great features available in &kmail;"
msgstr "अत्र &kmail;"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You do not have to use your mouse when working with &kmail;. Everything can "
"be done with <link linkend=\"keyboard-shortcuts\">Keyboard Shortcuts</link>."
msgstr ""
"&amp;kmail; इत्यनेन सह कार्यं कुर्वन् भवता मूषकस्य उपयोगः न करणीयः । सर्वं सह कर्तुं "
"शक्यते<link linkend=\"keyboard-shortcuts\"> कीबोर्ड शॉर्टकट</link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although &kmail; is very reliable, you should keep backups of your messages, "
"&ie;, use one of the export/archive options listed in <link linkend=\"backups"
"\">Backup Options</link> to back up your settings and email regularly."
msgstr ""
"यद्यपि &amp;kmail; अतीव विश्वसनीयः अस्ति, भवान् स्वसन्देशानां बैकअपं स्थापयितव्यः, &amp;"
"ie;, सूचीकृतेषु निर्यात/संग्रहविकल्पेषु एकस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु<link linkend=\"backups\"> "
"बैकअप विकल्पाः</link> नियमितरूपेण भवतः सेटिंग्स् तथा ईमेल इत्यस्य बैकअपं ग्रहीतुं।"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; makes it easy to import email from many different email "
"applications. The options are described in <link linkend=\"import-restore"
"\">Restore and Import in &kmail;</link>."
msgstr ""
"&amp;kmail; अनेकेभ्यः भिन्नेभ्यः ईमेल-अनुप्रयोगेभ्यः ईमेल-आयातं सुलभं करोति । विकल्पाः "
"वर्णिताः सन्ति<link linkend=\"import-restore\"> &amp;kmail इत्यत्र पुनर्स्थापनं आयातं "
"च कुर्वन्तु;</link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can separate your messages into different categories by using &kmail;'s "
"extensive <link linkend=\"folders\">Folders</link> options. Features include "
"special handling for specified folders: mailing lists, acl (&IMAP; only), "
"and archiving."
msgstr ""
"&amp;kmail;&#39;s extensive इत्यस्य उपयोगेन भवान् स्वसन्देशान् भिन्नवर्गेषु पृथक् कर्तुं "
"शक्नोति<link linkend=\"folders\"> पुटम्</link> विकल्पाः। विशेषतासु निर्दिष्टपुटस्य "
"विशेषनियन्त्रणं भवति: मेलसूची, acl (&amp;IMAP; केवलं), संग्रहणं च ।"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can complement your folder setup with highly configurable <link linkend="
"\"filters\">filters</link>."
msgstr ""
"भवान् अत्यन्तं विन्यासयोग्येन स्वस्य पुटस्य सेटअपस्य पूरकं कर्तुं शक्नोति<link linkend=\"filters"
"\"> छानकाः</link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &kmail; will detect common email <link linkend=\"configure-"
"security-email-scams\">scams</link>. You can also fight SPAM and viruses by "
"creating filters that work with external programs to scan email as it comes "
"in. See <link linkend=\"the-anti-spam-wizard\">Anti Spam</link> and <link "
"linkend=\"the-anti-virus-wizard\">Anti Virus</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण &amp;kmail; सामान्यं ईमेलं ज्ञास्यति<link linkend=\"configure-"
"security-email-scams\"> घोटाले</link> . भवन्तः SPAM तथा वायरसयोः विरुद्धं युद्धं कर्तुं "
"शक्नुवन्ति यत् बाह्यप्रोग्रामैः सह कार्यं कुर्वन्ति फ़िल्टर्स् निर्माय ईमेलं यथा आगच्छति तथा स्कैन् "
"कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति पश्यन्तु<link linkend=\"the-anti-spam-wizard\"> स्पैमविरोधी</link> "
"तथा<link linkend=\"the-anti-virus-wizard\"> एंटी वायरस</link> विस्तरेण कृते।"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It's easy to manage several email accounts by using different <link linkend="
"\"configure-identity\">identities</link>."
msgstr ""
"भिन्न-भिन्न-उपयोगेन अनेक-ईमेल-खातानां प्रबन्धनं सुलभम् अस्ति<link linkend=\"configure-"
"identity\"> तादात्म्यम्</link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "We hope you will enjoy &kmail;!"
msgstr "आशास्महे यत् भवद्भ्यः &kmail;!"

#. Tag: title
#: intro.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting Help"
msgstr "सहायतां प्राप्तुं"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kmail;'s homepage can be found at <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/"
#| "Special:MyLanguage/KMail\">https://userbase.kde.org/KMail</ulink>. There "
#| "you will find useful links (&eg;, to the user and developer mailing "
#| "lists, and to the community wiki pages.) Please report any bugs in "
#| "&kmail; using <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Report "
#| "Bug...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"&kmail;'s homepage can be found at <ulink url=\"https://apps.kde.org/kmail2/"
"\">https://apps.kde.org/kmail2/</ulink>. There you will find useful links "
"(&eg;, to the user and developer mailing lists, and to the community wiki "
"pages.) Please report any bugs in &kmail; using <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Report Bug...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; इत्यस्य मुखपृष्ठं <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:MyLanguage/"
"KMail\">https://userbase.kde.org/KMail</ulink> इत्यत्र प्राप्यते । तत्र भवन्तः "
"उपयोगिनो लिङ्कानि (&kmail; <menuchoice><guimenu>सहायता</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>दोषस्य प्रतिवेदनं कुर्वन्तु...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> इत्यस्य "
"उपयोगेन ।"
